    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="前端生成小程序码"><a href="#前端生成小程序码" class="headerlink" title="前端生成小程序码"></a>前端生成小程序码</h3><a id="more"></a><font>   业务场景: 邀请用户;<br>   access_token是必须的参数，需要后台传给你。<br>   js代码</font><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Page(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    data:&#123;&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    onLoad:function(e)&#123;&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    onShow:function(e)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      // 假如后台已经把access_token传给你；</span><br><span class="line">      var access_token = that.data.access_token;</span><br><span class="line">      var userId = that.data.userId;</span><br><span class="line">        wx.request(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            method: &quot;POST&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">            responseType: &apos;arraybuffer&apos;,</span><br><span class="line">            url: &apos;https://api.weixin.qq.com/wxa/getwxacodeunlimit?access_token=&apos;+access_token,</span><br><span class="line">            data:&#123;</span><br><span class="line">              scene:&apos;000&apos;,</span><br><span class="line">              path: &apos;pages/me/register/register?userId=&apos; + userId,</span><br><span class="line">              width:430</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            success:function(res)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">              var src2 = wx.arrayBufferToBase64(res.data);获取到的数据需要转换成二维码图片</span><br><span class="line">              that.setData(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                src2:src2</span><br><span class="line">              &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">          &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;image src=&apos;data:image/png;base64,&#123;&#123;src2&#125;&#125;&apos; mode=&quot;widthFix&quot;&gt;&lt;/image&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="小程序请求封装"><a href="#小程序请求封装" class="headerlink" title="小程序请求封装"></a>小程序请求封装</h3><p><font>此处是封装的微信小程序请求方法</font></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">function commonAjax(url, types, data) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  url:api请求地址</span><br><span class="line">  types：请求类型</span><br><span class="line">  data：请求参数键值对 &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">   var app = getApp()</span><br><span class="line">   var promise = new Promise(function (resolve, reject, defaults) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    wx.request(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        url: app.globalData.http_post_prefix + url,</span><br><span class="line">        data: data,</span><br><span class="line">        dataType: &quot;json&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">        method: (types === 1) ? &apos;GET&apos; : &apos;POST&apos;,</span><br><span class="line">        header: (types === 1) ? &#123; &apos;content-type&apos;: &apos;application/json&apos; &#125; : &#123; &apos;content-type&apos;: &apos;application/x-www-form-urlencoded&apos; &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">        success: resolve,</span><br><span class="line">        fail: reject,</span><br><span class="line">        complete: defaults,</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;)</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">  return promise;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">module.exports = &#123;</span><br><span class="line"> commonAjax:commonAjax</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><font>在其他页面的调用：封装方法放入until</font></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">var untils = require(&apos;../../until/until&apos;)</span><br><span class="line">Page(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  data&#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">  onLoad:function()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    let data=&#123;a:1,b:2&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    untils.commonAjax(&apos;www.baidu.com&apos;,1,data)</span><br><span class="line">    .then(function(res)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">       //to do something</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="前端调小程序地图"><a href="#前端调小程序地图" class="headerlink" title="前端调小程序地图"></a>前端调小程序地图</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">bindSelectAddresstap: function () &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    //获取用户的授权</span><br><span class="line">    wx.authorize(&#123;scope: &apos;res&apos;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">    //获取用户当前定位地址 经纬度</span><br><span class="line">    wx.chooseLocation(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      success: res =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        this.setData(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        address: res.address,</span><br><span class="line">        longitude: res.longitude,</span><br><span class="line">        latitude: res.latitude</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">      //当用户拒绝授权再次点击时进入收授权页面再次授权。</span><br><span class="line">      fail: res =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        wx.showModal(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">          title: &apos;温馨提示&apos;,</span><br><span class="line">          content: &apos;您已拒绝授权，是否去设置打开？&apos;,</span><br><span class="line">          confirmText: &quot;确认&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">          cancelText: &quot;取消&quot;,</span><br><span class="line">        success: res =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">          if (res.confirm) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            wx.openSetting(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">              success: (res) =&gt; &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              console.log(res)</span><br><span class="line">              res.authSetting = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">              &quot;scope.userLocation&quot;: true,</span><br><span class="line">              &#125;</span><br><span class="line">              console.log(&quot;openSetting: success&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">              &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; else &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">&#125;,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="数组去重封装"><a href="#数组去重封装" class="headerlink" title="数组去重封装"></a>数组去重封装</h3><p><font>促销信息重复的时候，根据促销信息的类型属性去重</font></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">let arr = [</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;type:1,desc:&apos;购买此商品10个赠送2&apos;&#125;，</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;type:1,desc:&apos;购买此商品5个赠送1&apos;&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;type:2,desc:&apos;购买此商品100元打8折&apos;&#125;，</span><br><span class="line">  &#123;type:2,desc&apos;购买此商品50元打9折&apos;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">]</span><br><span class="line">let hash = &#123;&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">arr = arr.reduce(function (item, next) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">hash[next.type] ? &apos;&apos; : hash[next.type] = true &amp;&amp; item.push(next);</span><br><span class="line">return item</span><br><span class="line">&#125;, [])</span><br><span class="line">&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">`</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><font>数组值的去重</font></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">let arr = [1,2,3,33,55,44,1,44,55,33]</span><br><span class="line">function unique(arr) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    return Array.from(new Set(arr));</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">unique(arr)</span><br><span class="line">获取到[1,2,3,33,44,55]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="获取用户头像-昵称"><a href="#获取用户头像-昵称" class="headerlink" title="获取用户头像 昵称"></a>获取用户头像 昵称</h3><p><font>无须经过请求api，直接获取</font></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;open-data type=&quot;userAvatarUrl&quot;&gt;&lt;/open-data&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;open-data type=&quot;userNickName&quot; lang=&quot;zh_CN&quot;&gt;&lt;/open-data&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
