    <title>小程序 仿淘宝商品详情选项卡吸顶</title>
    <link href="https://mwm0522.github.io/hexo/2019/10/09/miniprogram/"/>
    <id>https://mwm0522.github.io/hexo/2019/10/09/miniprogram/</id>
    <published>2019-10-09T12:59:38.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-10-20T10:44:00.321Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="wxml默认布局"><a href="#wxml默认布局" class="headerlink" title="wxml默认布局"></a>wxml默认布局</h3><a id="more"></a>  <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;view class=&quot;container&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;view class=&quot;banner&quot;&gt;&lt;/view&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;view class=&quot;tab &#123;&#123;bannerH&lt;scrollTop?&apos;fixNav&apos;:&apos;&apos;&#125;&#125;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;view bindtap=&quot;click&quot; data-index=&quot;0&quot; class=&quot;&#123;&#123;num==0?&apos;selected&apos;:&apos;&apos;&#125;&#125;&quot;&gt;宝贝&lt;/view&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;view bindtap=&quot;click&quot; data-index=&quot;1&quot; class=&quot;&#123;&#123;num==1?&apos;selected&apos;:&apos;&apos;&#125;&#125;&quot;&gt;详情&lt;/view&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;view bindtap=&quot;click&quot; data-index=&quot;2&quot; class=&quot;&#123;&#123;num==2?&apos;selected&apos;:&apos;&apos;&#125;&#125;&quot;&gt;评论&lt;/view&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      &lt;view bindtap=&quot;click&quot; data-index=&quot;3&quot; class=&quot;&#123;&#123;num==3?&apos;selected&apos;:&apos;&apos;&#125;&#125;&quot;&gt;推荐商品&lt;/view&gt;</span><br><span class="line"> &lt;/view&gt;</span><br><span class="line"> &lt;view class=&quot;tab_content&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;view wx:if=&quot;&#123;&#123;num==0&#125;&#125;&quot;&gt;宝贝&lt;/view&gt; </span><br><span class="line">    &lt;view wx:if=&quot;&#123;&#123;num==1&#125;&#125;&quot;&gt;详情&lt;/view&gt; </span><br><span class="line">    &lt;view wx:if=&quot;&#123;&#123;num==2&#125;&#125;&quot;&gt;评论&lt;/view&gt; </span><br><span class="line">    &lt;view wx:if=&quot;&#123;&#123;num==3&#125;&#125;&quot;&gt;推荐商品&lt;/view&gt; </span><br><span class="line"> &lt;/view&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/view&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="js逻辑处理"><a href="#js逻辑处理" class="headerlink" title="js逻辑处理"></a>js逻辑处理</h3>  <font>    分析: <br>    ①选项卡的制作。<br>    ②页面的高度大于banner元素高度时候，tab元素内容应固定在页面顶部，反之回到原来位置。  </font>   <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Page(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    data:&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        tab:[&#123;name:&apos;宝贝&apos;&#125;,&#123; name: &apos;详情&apos; &#125;,&#123; name: &apos;评论&apos; &#125;,&#123; name: &apos;推荐&apos; &#125;]</span><br><span class="line">        num:0</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    onLoad:function(options)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">     //获取banner元素高度</span><br><span class="line">      var that = this;</span><br><span class="line">      const query = wx.createSelectorQuery();</span><br><span class="line">      query.select(&apos;.banner&apos;).boundingClientRect();</span><br><span class="line">      query.exec(function(rect)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">           that.setData(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">               bannerH:rect[0].height</span><br><span class="line">           &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    click:function(e)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      this.setData(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">          num: e.currentTarget.dataset.index</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    //获取页面滚动高度</span><br><span class="line">    onPageScroll:function(e)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        that.setData(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            scrollTop:e.scrollTop</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="wxss布局"><a href="#wxss布局" class="headerlink" title="wxss布局"></a>wxss布局</h3>   <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.tab&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    display:flex;</span><br><span class="line">    justify-content:space-between;</span><br><span class="line">    align-items:center;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">.fixNav&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    position:fixed</span><br><span class="line">    top:0,</span><br><span class="line">    width:100%;</span><br><span class="line">    z-index:9999;</span><br><span class="line">    background-color:#fff;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
